# PM Research: Content/Posts System

**Task:** `2025-12-16__CONTENT-POSTS-SYSTEM`  
**Prepared By:** Product Operations Agent  
**Date:** December 16, 2025  
**Status:** ✅ Complete

---

## Executive Summary

This task implements the core content system for NuttyFans, enabling creators to publish posts with media (images, videos) and users to engage through a personalized feed.

---

## Feature Scope

| Feature | Priority | PRD Reference |
|---------|----------|---------------|
| Post Creation | P0 | C-010, C-011, C-012 |
| Media Upload (S3) | P0 | C-010, C-011 |
| Video Processing (Mux) | P0 | PRD 3.2.2 |
| Access Control (free/sub/PPV) | P0 | C-013, C-014 |
| Post Scheduling | P0 | C-015 |
