---

## User Stories

### Creator Stories

- C-010: Upload images to share visual content
- C-011: Upload videos to share video content
- C-012: Write text posts for updates
- C-013: Set posts as free/paid to control access
- C-014: Set PPV prices for individual posts
- C-015: Schedule posts for future publishing
- C-016: Post stories for ephemeral content
- C-018: Post short videos (reels)
- C-042: Watermarked content for leak tracing

### User Stories

- U-010: Browse feed from subscribed creators
- U-030: Like posts to show appreciation
- U-031: Comment on posts to interact
- U-032: Bookmark posts for later

---

## Technical Requirements

### Post Types

| Type | Max Size | Formats | Duration |
|------|----------|---------|----------|
| Image | 20MB | JPG, PNG, GIF, WebP | N/A |
| Video | 5GB | MP4, MOV, WebM | 60 min |
| Text | 5000 chars | Markdown | N/A |
| Story | 50MB | Image/Video | 24h |
| Reel | 500MB | MP4 | 3 min |

### Video Processing (Mux)

- Auto-transcode to 480p, 720p, 1080p
- Thumbnail generation
- Preview clip generation
- HLS/DASH streaming

### Access Levels

| Level | Visibility |
|-------|------------|
| `free` | Anyone can view |
| `subscribers` | Active subscribers only |
| `ppv` | Pay to unlock ($1-$500) |

---

## Confirmed Decisions

| Decision | Answer | Rationale |
|----------|--------|-----------|
| Video Provider | Mux | Managed, simple integration |
| Comments | MVP | User engagement critical |
| Stories/Reels | MVP | Competitive with Instagram/TikTok |
| Watermark | Invisible | Better UX, still traceable |

